      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride! This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it, making it a fantastic choice for anyone looking for a solid, functional vehicle at a great value. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its journeys, it remains a reliable companion that's ready to take you where you need to go. With a little TLC, this car will continue to serve you well for years to come!",
