    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for a budget-friendly option. Mechanically, the car is reliable and starts up without issue, though a prospective buyer should be prepared for some upcoming routine maintenance and potential minor repairs as it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat, and the interior shows typical wear and tear on the upholstery and plastic trim. Despite these cosmetic and age-related imperfections, the car remains functional and offers a solid value for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
