    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera features a robust 3.6L flat-six boxer engine paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical assembly remains tight, with the M96 powerplant delivering linear torque across the rev range. Equipped with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) for active damping control and four-piston monoblock fixed calipers, the braking and handling dynamics are quintessential Porsche. Recent service includes a borescope inspection and oil analysis to confirm internal health. The chassis exhibits excellent torsional rigidity, and the drivetrain provides predictable exit traction via its rear-engine bias. A driver-spec example that prioritizes mechanical integrity and analog engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
