    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been kept in impressive condition by a conscientious owner. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine pulls strong with no hesitations, and the suspension remains tight and responsive through corners. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, though closer inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats show only light softening on the entry bolsters, and every feature, including the panoramic sunroof and the upgraded infotainment system, works exactly as intended. It comes with a full set of service records, two keys, and tires that were replaced less than 5,000 miles ago. This is a turn-key car ready for its next chapter.",
